<section class="talent-review" aria-label="统一考核标准如何误判专项人才">
  <header class="review-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">VALUE DISTORTION</span>
    <h2>一个人，如何被一张统一清单误判</h2>
    <p>问题不在于能力要求多，而在于一旦制度变成“缺一项就卡级”，人的长板就会被短板覆盖。</p>
  </header>

  <div class="distortion-board">
    <article class="ability-panel">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <span class="panel-index">01</span>
        <div>
          <strong>真实能力结构</strong>
          <span>这个人不是平均型选手，而是明显偏科</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ability-list">
        <div class="ability-row">
          <span>传统表格工具</span>
          <div class="ability-track"><i style="--level: 38%"></i></div>
          <b>一般</b>
        </div>
        <div class="ability-row">
          <span>推广投放</span>
          <div class="ability-track"><i style="--level: 30%"></i></div>
          <b>较弱</b>
        </div>
        <div class="ability-row strong-row">
          <span>AI 数据可视化</span>
          <div class="ability-track"><i style="--level: 94%"></i></div>
          <b>很强</b>
        </div>
        <div class="ability-row strong-row">
          <span>自动化与流程</span>
          <div class="ability-track"><i style="--level: 98%"></i></div>
          <b>很强</b>
        </div>
        <div class="ability-row value-row">
          <span>实际产出</span>
          <div class="ability-track"><i style="--level: 96%"></i></div>
          <b>高</b>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <div class="verdict-column" aria-label="制度误判路径">
      <span class="verdict-chip">统一清单</span>
      <span class="verdict-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
      <strong>缺项</strong>
      <small>不会高级表格<br />不会推广</small>
      <span class="verdict-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
      <div class="blocked-badge">卡在初级</div>
    </div>

    <article class="result-panel">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <span class="panel-index">02</span>
        <div>
          <strong>制度给出的结论</strong>
          <span>长板只算加分，短板却拥有否决权</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="result-stack">
        <div class="result-item danger">
          <span>工资等级</span>
          <strong>被基础项锁住</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="result-item">
          <span>真实贡献</span>
          <strong>一人可承担多人重复工作</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="result-item">
          <span>成长方向</span>
          <strong>被迫补齐平均线</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="loss-strip">
    <div>
      <span>制度看见的</span>
      <strong>“你还有两项不会”</strong>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span>公司真正拥有的</span>
      <strong>一个高杠杆专项人才</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="loss-cell">
      <span>最后被浪费的</span>
      <strong>最可能形成竞争力的长板</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="career-model">
    <header>
      <span class="eyebrow">BETTER MODEL</span>
      <h3>更合理的模型：一个底座，多条上升路线</h3>
