    </header>

    <div class="common-base">
      <span>共同底线</span>
      <strong>平台规则 · 基础数据理解 · 独立执行 · 基本协作</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="track-grid">
      <article><span>经营</span><strong>推广投放</strong></article>
      <article><span>分析</span><strong>数据洞察</strong></article>
      <article class="focus-track"><span>杠杆</span><strong>AI / 自动化</strong></article>
      <article><span>表达</span><strong>内容视觉</strong></article>
      <article><span>业务</span><strong>商品供应链</strong></article>
      <article><span>范围</span><strong>团队管理</strong></article>
    </div>

    <footer class="evaluation-logic">
      <span>最终评价不再问“是否全部会”</span>
      <div>
        <strong>专业深度</strong>
        <i>+</i>
        <strong>实际产出</strong>
        <i>+</i>
        <strong>责任范围</strong>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

